{
  "title": "第2周 第4天 — 名词复数：阴性名词复数 (-и/-і)",
  "objective": "<strong>学习目标：</strong>掌握阴性名词的复数变化规则（-а→-и、-я→-і、-ь→-і），学会17个新阴性名词及其复数形式，并能对比阳性与阴性的复数规则。",
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "grammar",
      "heading": "1. 回顾：阳性名词复数",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>上节课要点回顾</h3><p>阳性名词（辅音结尾）变复数的核心规则：</p><ul><li><strong>硬辅音结尾 → 加 -и</strong>：<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"兄弟\">брат</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">брати</span>，<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"大学生\">студент</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">студенти</span>，<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"建筑\">будинок</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">будинки</span></li><li><strong>软辅音/ж/ч/ш/щ/ц 结尾 → 加 -і</strong>：<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"铅笔\">олівець</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">олівці</span>，<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"钥匙\">ключ</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">ключі</span>，<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"医生\">лікар</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">лікарі</span></li><li><strong>特殊变化</strong>：<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"朋友\">друг</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">друзі</span>（г→з），<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"学生\">учень</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">учні</span>（去 -ь 加 -і）</li></ul>"
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "html": "<strong>快速回忆口诀：</strong>阳性复数看结尾 — 硬辅加 -и，软辅/嘶嘶音加 -і。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "grammar",
      "heading": "2. 语法讲解：阴性名词复数规则",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "今天我们学习阴性名词如何变成复数。阴性名词的复数变化比阳性更加规则，核心思路是<strong>\u201c去掉词尾，加上新词尾\u201d</strong>。"
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>规则1：-а 结尾 → 去掉 -а，加 -и</h3><p>这是最常见的阴性复数规则。大量以 -а 结尾的阴性名词都遵循此规则。</p><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>复数</th><th>中文</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"学校\">школа</td><td class=\"uk-word\">школи</td><td>学校</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"书\">книга</td><td class=\"uk-word\">книги</td><td>书</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"汽车\">машина</td><td class=\"uk-word\">машини</td><td>汽车</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"工作\">робота</td><td class=\"uk-word\">роботи</td><td>工作</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"路\">дорога</td><td class=\"uk-word\">дороги</td><td>路</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>记忆技巧：</strong>就像中文里\u201c一所学校 → 很多学校\u201d，乌克兰语只是把 -а 换成 -и，非常简单！</p><p><strong>包含 -ка 的词 → -ки：</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>复数</th><th>中文</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"花\">квітка</td><td class=\"uk-word\">квітки</td><td>花</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"星星\">зірка</td><td class=\"uk-word\">зірки</td><td>星星</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"勺子\">ложка</td><td class=\"uk-word\">ложки</td><td>勺子</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>包含 -га 的词 → -ги：</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>复数</th><th>中文</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"腿\">нога</td><td class=\"uk-word\">ноги</td><td>脚/腿</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"女性朋友\">подруга</td><td class=\"uk-word\">подруги</td><td>女性朋友</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "html": "<strong>注意：</strong>不管 -а 前面是什么辅音（к、г、н、т……），规则都一样 — 去 -а 加 -и。-ка→-ки、-га→-ги、-на→-ни，规律完全一致。"
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>规则2：-я 结尾 → 去掉 -я，加 -і</h3><p>以 -я 结尾的阴性名词，复数时去掉 -я，加上 -і。注意这里加的是 <strong>-і</strong>（不是 -и），因为 -я 前面通常是软辅音。</p><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>复数</th><th>中文</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"厨房\">кухня</td><td class=\"uk-word\">кухні</td><td>厨房</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"歌曲\">пісня</td><td class=\"uk-word\">пісні</td><td>歌曲</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"家庭\">сім'я</td><td class=\"uk-word\">сім'ї</td><td>家庭</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"梦想\">мрія</td><td class=\"uk-word\">мрії</td><td>梦想</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>-ця 结尾 → -ці：</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>复数</th><th>中文</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"街道\">вулиця</td><td class=\"uk-word\">вулиці</td><td>街道</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"女学生\">учениця</td><td class=\"uk-word\">учениці</td><td>女学生</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>-ія 结尾 → -ії：</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>复数</th><th>中文</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"车站\">станція</td><td class=\"uk-word\">станції</td><td>车站</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"历史\">історія</td><td class=\"uk-word\">історії</td><td>历史</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"职业\">професія</td><td class=\"uk-word\">професії</td><td>职业</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "html": "<strong>对比记忆：</strong><ul><li>-а 结尾 → 加 <strong>-и</strong>（硬元音）：<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"学校\">школа</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">школи</span></li><li>-я 结尾 → 加 <strong>-і</strong>（软元音）：<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"厨房\">кухня</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">кухні</span></li></ul><p>口诀：<strong>硬-а配-и，软-я配-і</strong>。和阳性复数的逻辑一样（硬辅音加-и，软辅音加-і），乌克兰语的\u201c硬软配对\u201d非常一致！</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>规则3：-ь 结尾的阴性名词 → 去掉 -ь，加 -і</h3><p>以 -ь 结尾的<strong>阴性</strong>名词，变复数时去掉 -ь，加 -і。</p><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>复数</th><th>中文</th><th>备注</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"影子\">тінь</td><td class=\"uk-word\">тіні</td><td>影子</td><td>规则变化</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"喜悦\">радість</td><td class=\"uk-word\">радості</td><td>喜悦</td><td>-ість → -ості</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"新闻\">новість</td><td class=\"uk-word\">новості</td><td>新闻</td><td>-ість → -ості</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"可能性\">можливість</td><td class=\"uk-word\">можливості</td><td>可能性</td><td>-ість → -ості</td></tr><tr><td class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"速度\">швидкість</td><td class=\"uk-word\">швидкості</td><td>速度</td><td>-ість → -ості</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>-ість → -ості</strong> 是一个非常规律的模式：只要看到 -ість 结尾的阴性名词，复数一定是 -ості。</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "error-warn",
          "html": "<strong>注意元音交替现象！</strong><p>少数以 -ь 结尾的阴性名词在变复数时会发生<strong>元音交替</strong>（і→о 或 і→е）：</p><ul><li><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"夜晚\">ніч</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">ночі</span>（夜晚：і→о！）</li><li><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"盐\">сіль</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">солі</span>（盐：і→о！）</li><li><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"秋天\">осінь</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">осені</span>（秋天：і→е！）</li></ul><p>这些需要特别记忆，好在数量不多。</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>阴性复数规则总结</h3><table><thead><tr><th>词尾</th><th>变化方式</th><th>示例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>-а</td><td>去 -а 加 -и</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"学校\">школа</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">школи</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ка</td><td>→ -ки</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"花\">квітка</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">квітки</span></td></tr><tr><td>-га</td><td>→ -ги</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"腿\">нога</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">ноги</span></td></tr><tr><td>-я</td><td>去 -я 加 -і</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"厨房\">кухня</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">кухні</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ця</td><td>→ -ці</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"街道\">вулиця</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">вулиці</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ія</td><td>→ -ії</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"车站\">станція</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">станції</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ь (阴性)</td><td>去 -ь 加 -і</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"喜悦\">радість</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">радості</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ість</td><td>→ -ості</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"新闻\">новість</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">новості</span></td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "html": "<strong>阳性 vs 阴性复数对比记忆：</strong><table><thead><tr><th>性别</th><th>变化</th><th>示例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>阳性（硬辅音）</td><td>加 -и</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"兄弟\">брат</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">брати</span></td></tr><tr><td>阳性（软辅音）</td><td>加 -і</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"铅笔\">олівець</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">олівці</span></td></tr><tr><td>阴性（-а）</td><td>去-а 加-и</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"学校\">школа</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">школи</span></td></tr><tr><td>阴性（-я）</td><td>去-я 加-і</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"厨房\">кухня</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">кухні</span></td></tr></tbody></table><p>规律：<strong>硬音配 -и，软音配 -і</strong>，不管阳性还是阴性！</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
